contentrichtext.text: {{TOCright}} '''Annan''' may refer to: ==People== *[[Annan (surname)]] * Annan, sometimes referred to as [[Chintō]], taught the [[kata]] (martial arts) to [[Matsumura Sōkon]] ==Places== ;Australia * Annan River, Queensland, a river just south of Cooktown ;Scotland * [[Annan, Dumfries and Galloway]] ** [[Annan Academy]], a secondary school ** [[Annan Athletic F.C.]], a football club * [[River Annan]], Dumfries and Galloway ;Taiwan * [[Annan District]], a district located in the north of Tainan City ==Politics== * [[Annan Plan for Cyprus]], United Nations proposal to reunify Cyprus ==See also== *[[Annam (disambiguation)]] *[[Annandale]] *[[Anann]], a goddess in Irish mythology {{disambiguation|geo}}
